{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "edu-cram-teacher-teaching-classroom-x7yy",
    "category": "pro/education/cram_teacher",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7yYE6Me9w8",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, hey, slow down there, Finney. I know you're excited for your first day of school.",
      "zh": "嘿，嘿，放慢點，芬尼。我知道你對第一天上學很興奮。",
      "ja": "ねえねえ、ちょっと落ち着いて、フィニー。初めての登校日でワクワクしているのはわかるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't wait. Is it time to go yet? Is it?",
      "zh": "我等不及了。現在可以出發了嗎？可以了嗎？",
      "ja": "待ちきれないよ。もう行く時間？もう？",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Not yet, Finney. We have a little surprise for you.",
      "zh": "還沒，芬尼。我們有個小驚喜給你。",
      "ja": "まだだよ、フィニー。ちょっとしたサプライズがあるんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A new lunchbox.",
      "zh": "一個新的便當盒。",
      "ja": "新しいお弁当箱だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wonder Shark. She's my favorite.",
      "zh": "奇蹟鯊魚。她是我最喜歡的。",
      "ja": "ワンダーシャーク。彼女が一番好き。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mama and Papa.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，媽媽和爸爸。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ママとパパ。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome. Okay. Now it's time for you to go. Do you have all your things?",
      "zh": "不客氣。好了，現在該你出發了。你帶齊東西了嗎？",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。さあ、そろそろ行く時間だよ。持ち物は全部ある？",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lunchbox?",
      "zh": "便當盒？",
      "ja": "お弁当箱？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Check.",
      "zh": "有。",
      "ja": "あるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Backpack? Check.",
      "zh": "背包？有。",
      "ja": "リュックは？あるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Kiss goodbye.",
      "zh": "親吻道別。",
      "ja": "バイバイのキス。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And where? Check.",
      "zh": "還有哪裡？有。",
      "ja": "それからどこ？あるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right. Let's go to school.",
      "zh": "好吧，我們去學校吧。",
      "ja": "よし、学校に行こう。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time for school. Doo-doo-do- doo-doo-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do-do",
      "zh": "上學時間。嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟嘟",
      "ja": "学校の時間だ。ドゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥードゥー",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time for school.",
      "zh": "上學時間。",
      "ja": "学校の時間だ。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, hello Finney.",
      "zh": "哦，你好，芬尼。",
      "ja": "ああ、こんにちはフィニー。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think I know where you're headed.",
      "zh": "我想我知道你要去哪裡。",
      "ja": "君がどこに向かっているか分かるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me help you get there.",
      "zh": "讓我幫你去那裡。",
      "ja": "そこまで案内してあげよう。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Better hurry.",
      "zh": "最好快點。",
      "ja": "急いだほうがいいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here's your school.",
      "zh": "這是你的學校。",
      "ja": "ここが君の学校だ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, bye, Mama.",
      "zh": "好，拜拜，媽媽。",
      "ja": "うん、バイバイ、ママ。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait one second, my little Finny.",
      "zh": "等一下，我的小芬尼。",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って、僕の小さなフィニー。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think you forgot something.",
      "zh": "我想你忘了什麼。",
      "ja": "何か忘れていると思うよ。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, right.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now, bye-bye, Mama.",
      "zh": "現在，拜拜，媽媽。",
      "ja": "じゃあ、バイバイ、ママ。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a good first day, Finny.",
      "zh": "祝你第一天愉快，芬尼。",
      "ja": "初登校、楽しんでね、フィニー。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "In my favorite class, we'll probably be sons.",
      "zh": "在我最喜歡的班級，我們可能會是兒子們。",
      "ja": "僕の好きなクラスで、たぶん僕たちは息子たちだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm actually already alone.",
      "zh": "其實我已經一個人了。",
      "ja": "実はもう一人ぼっちだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um, excuse me?",
      "zh": "嗯，請問？",
      "ja": "あの、すみません？",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is this, uh...",
      "zh": "這是，呃...",
      "ja": "これは、えっと...",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Myrtle?",
      "zh": "默特爾？",
      "ja": "マートル？",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Myrtle the turtle? Is that you?",
      "zh": "烏龜默特爾？是你嗎？",
      "ja": "カメのマートル？君？",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, Finny.",
      "zh": "哦，芬尼。",
      "ja": "ああ、フィニー。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I didn't see you there.",
      "zh": "我沒看到你。",
      "ja": "気づかなかったよ。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, it's me.",
      "zh": "是的，是我。",
      "ja": "そう、僕だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are we going to be in the same class?",
      "zh": "我們會在同一班嗎？",
      "ja": "同じクラスになるの？",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think so.",
      "zh": "我想是的。",
      "ja": "そう思うよ。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, you.",
      "zh": "哦，你。",
      "ja": "ああ、君。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was worried I wouldn't know anyone here.",
      "zh": "我擔心我在這裡不認識任何人。",
      "ja": "ここで誰も知らないかと思って心配だった。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm a little nervous.",
      "zh": "我有點緊張。",
      "ja": "ちょっと緊張してる。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey.",
      "zh": "哦，嘿。",
      "ja": "ああ、やあ。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Shelley.",
      "zh": "我是雪莉。",
      "ja": "僕はシェリー。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's my first day of school, too.",
      "zh": "我也是第一天上學。",
      "ja": "僕も初登校だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What are your dates?",
      "zh": "你們是誰？",
      "ja": "君たちは誰？",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Finny.",
      "zh": "我是芬尼。",
      "ja": "僕はフィニー。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And this is Myrtle.",
      "zh": "這是默特爾。",
      "ja": "そしてこっちがマートル。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Myrtle?",
      "zh": "默特爾？",
      "ja": "マートル？",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "zh": "哦，是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Chloe.",
      "zh": "我是克洛伊。",
      "ja": "僕はクロエ。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Fiona.",
      "zh": "我是菲奧娜。",
      "ja": "僕はフィオナ。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Sandy.",
      "zh": "我是桑迪。",
      "ja": "僕はサンディ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My name's Wheel.",
      "zh": "我叫威爾。",
      "ja": "僕の名前はウィール。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, Finny, are you a shark?",
      "zh": "那麼，芬尼，你是鯊魚嗎？",
      "ja": "それで、フィニー、君はサメ？",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um, yes, I am.",
      "zh": "嗯，是的，我是。",
      "ja": "うん、そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa, that is so cool.",
      "zh": "哇，那真酷。",
      "ja": "わあ、それはかっこいいね。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So you're a shark, huh?",
      "zh": "所以你是鯊魚，對吧？",
      "ja": "じゃあ君はサメなんだね？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, I'm Oscar.",
      "zh": "嗯，我是奧斯卡。",
      "ja": "僕はオスカーだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm an octopus.",
      "zh": "我是一隻章魚。",
      "ja": "僕はタコだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I know all about sharks.",
      "zh": "我對鯊魚瞭若指掌。",
      "ja": "サメのことは全部知ってるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like, did you know that if a shark's tooth falls out,",
      "zh": "你知道鯊魚掉牙後，",
      "ja": "例えば、サメの歯が抜けたら、",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "a new one will grow in its place?",
      "zh": "會長出一顆新的牙齒嗎？",
      "ja": "新しい歯が生えてくるんだよ？",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ooh, does the new one grow in even sharper?",
      "zh": "喔，那新牙會長得更鋒利嗎？",
      "ja": "おお、新しい歯はもっと鋭くなるの？",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you have super sharp teeth?",
      "zh": "你有超鋒利的牙齒嗎？",
      "ja": "君は超鋭い歯を持ってる？",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見せて。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見せて。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "うんうん。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello, everyone.",
      "zh": "大家好。",
      "ja": "みなさん、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My name is Mr. Magellan.",
      "zh": "我叫麥哲倫先生。",
      "ja": "私はマゼラン先生です。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll be a teacher this year.",
      "zh": "今年我會是你們的老師。",
      "ja": "今年は先生を務めます。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're about to learn so many new things.",
      "zh": "你們將學到很多新東西。",
      "ja": "これからたくさんの新しいことを学びます。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come along to our classroom.",
      "zh": "跟我來教室吧。",
      "ja": "教室に来てください。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait for me.",
      "zh": "等我。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait for me.",
      "zh": "等我。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait for me.",
      "zh": "等我。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everybody find a disc.",
      "zh": "大家找一個圓盤。",
      "ja": "みんな、ディスクを見つけて。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "First things first.",
      "zh": "首先，",
      "ja": "まずはじめに、",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're going to get to know each other better,",
      "zh": "你們要更了解彼此，",
      "ja": "みんながお互いをもっと知るために、",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "by drawing some of our favorite things.",
      "zh": "透過畫出我們喜歡的東西。",
      "ja": "好きなものを描いてみよう。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like this.",
      "zh": "像這樣。",
      "ja": "こんな感じでね。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My favorite thing is called a telescope.",
      "zh": "我最喜歡的東西叫做望遠鏡。",
      "ja": "私の好きなものは望遠鏡です。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love to take my telescope up to the surface,",
      "zh": "我喜歡把望遠鏡帶到水面上，",
      "ja": "望遠鏡を水面に持っていくのが好きです。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "where I can use it to look at all the stars.",
      "zh": "用它來看所有的星星。",
      "ja": "それで星を全部見るんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love the moon surface.",
      "zh": "我喜歡月球表面。",
      "ja": "月の表面も好きです。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, grab some crayons.",
      "zh": "現在，拿些蠟筆。",
      "ja": "さあ、クレヨンを取って。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I want each of you to draw one of your favorite things.",
      "zh": "我希望你們每個人畫一樣你最喜歡的東西。",
      "ja": "みんな、それぞれ好きなものを一つ描いてください。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is everyone done?",
      "zh": "大家都畫好了嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな終わった？",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "zh": "是的！",
      "ja": "はい！",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is one for a second.",
      "zh": "這是第二個。",
      "ja": "これは2番目のやつ。",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And done.",
      "zh": "完成了。",
      "ja": "できた。",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, everyone put your drawings on the wall,",
      "zh": "現在，大家把畫貼在牆上，",
      "ja": "さあ、みんなの絵を壁に貼って、",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "so we can all see them.",
      "zh": "讓我們都能看到。",
      "ja": "みんなで見られるようにしよう。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Aren't you going to put up your drawing model?",
      "zh": "你不打算貼上你的畫嗎？",
      "ja": "自分の絵を貼らないの？",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um...",
      "zh": "嗯...",
      "ja": "えっと...",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at all these nice drawings.",
      "zh": "看看這些漂亮的畫。",
      "ja": "素敵な絵がいっぱいだね。",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who wants to start?",
      "zh": "誰想先開始？",
      "ja": "誰から始めたい？",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Me! Me!",
      "zh": "我！我！",
      "ja": "僕！僕！",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I draw library.",
      "zh": "我畫圖書館。",
      "ja": "図書館を描いたよ。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because you can learn lots and lots of neat things at the library.",
      "zh": "因為你可以在圖書館學到很多很棒的東西。",
      "ja": "図書館ではたくさんの素敵なことが学べるからね。",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good one, Oscar.",
      "zh": "好棒，奧斯卡。",
      "ja": "いいね、オスカー。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Libraries have books about all sorts of interesting things.",
      "zh": "圖書館有各種有趣的書籍。",
      "ja": "図書館にはいろんな面白い本があるよ。",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And what about your favorite thing, Leo?",
      "zh": "那你最喜歡的東西是什麼，利奧？",
      "ja": "レオ、君の好きなものは？",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I drew my pet clam clampy.",
      "zh": "我畫了我的寵物蛤蜊克蘭比。",
      "ja": "僕はペットのクラム、クランピーを描いたよ。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's shiny and beautiful.",
      "zh": "他閃亮又漂亮。",
      "ja": "彼はピカピカで美しいんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I love him so much.",
      "zh": "我非常愛他。",
      "ja": "とても大好きなんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great drawing, Leo.",
      "zh": "畫得真好，利奧。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい絵だね、レオ。",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sure you take very good care of Clampy.",
      "zh": "我相信你一定很照顧克蘭比。",
      "ja": "クランピーを大事にしているんだろうね。",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sammy?",
      "zh": "山米？",
      "ja": "サミー？",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's your turn.",
      "zh": "輪到你了。",
      "ja": "君の番だよ。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great, great.",
      "zh": "好，好。",
      "ja": "いいよ、いいよ。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because I drew a dinosaur with very, very, very sharp teeth.",
      "zh": "因為我畫了一隻牙齒非常非常鋒利的恐龍。",
      "ja": "とてもとても鋭い歯を持つ恐竜を描いたんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like dinosaurs because they are big and scary and grow.",
      "zh": "我喜歡恐龍，因為它們又大又可怕，還會大聲吼叫。",
      "ja": "恐竜が好きなんだ。大きくて怖くて、すごく大きな声で吠えるからね。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "really loud like this!",
      "zh": "就像這樣大聲！",
      "ja": "こんなに大きな声でね！",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, okay.",
      "zh": "好了，好了。",
      "ja": "はいはい。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Calm down, Sammy.",
      "zh": "冷靜點，山米。",
      "ja": "落ち着いて、サミー。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Finny, you're next.",
      "zh": "芬尼，你是下一個。",
      "ja": "フィニー、君の番だよ。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, um...",
      "zh": "哦，嗯...",
      "ja": "ああ、えっと...",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I drew my favorite superhero wonder shark.",
      "zh": "我畫了我最喜歡的超級英雄奇蹟鯊魚。",
      "ja": "僕は好きなスーパーヒーロー、ワンダーシャークを描いたよ。",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like her because she's very brief,",
      "zh": "我喜歡她，因為她很勇敢，",
      "ja": "彼女が好きなのは、とても勇敢だから。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "and helps all the fish in need.",
      "zh": "並且幫助所有需要幫助的魚。",
      "ja": "困っている魚たちを助けるから。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well done, Finny.",
      "zh": "做得好，芬尼。",
      "ja": "よくできました、フィニー。",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like wonder shark.",
      "zh": "我喜歡奇蹟鯊魚。",
      "ja": "ワンダーシャークが好き。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who's next?",
      "zh": "下一個是誰？",
      "ja": "次は誰？",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Meryl?",
      "zh": "默瑞爾？",
      "ja": "マーレル？",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Meryl?",
      "zh": "默瑞爾？",
      "ja": "マーレル？",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Where's Meryl?",
      "zh": "默瑞爾在哪裡？",
      "ja": "マーレルはどこ？",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Meryl?",
      "zh": "默瑞爾？",
      "ja": "マーレル？",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you nervous?",
      "zh": "你緊張嗎？",
      "ja": "緊張してる？",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because I was too.",
      "zh": "因為我也曾經緊張過。",
      "ja": "僕もそうだったよ。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But then, I just took a deep breath.",
      "zh": "但後來，我深呼吸了一下。",
      "ja": "でもその後、深呼吸をしたんだ。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I wasn't as nervous.",
      "zh": "我就不那麼緊張了。",
      "ja": "そうしたらあまり緊張しなくなった。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you sure?",
      "zh": "你確定嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I drew my favorite teddy.",
      "zh": "我畫了我最喜歡的泰迪熊。",
      "ja": "僕は好きなテディベアを描いたよ。",
      "time": "00:06:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Meryl Bear.",
      "zh": "默瑞爾熊。",
      "ja": "マーレルベア。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My grandpa gave him to me for my birthday.",
      "zh": "我爺爺在我生日送給我的。",
      "ja": "おじいちゃんが誕生日にくれたんだ。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's a very good teddy.",
      "zh": "他是一隻很棒的泰迪熊。",
      "ja": "とてもいいテディベアだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And adorable.",
      "zh": "而且很可愛。",
      "ja": "そしてかわいい。",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's so good.",
      "zh": "真好。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいね。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's so good.",
      "zh": "真好。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいね。",
      "time": "00:06:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good boy.",
      "zh": "乖孩子。",
      "ja": "いい子だね。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everyone loves your drawing, Myrtle.",
      "zh": "大家都喜歡你的畫，默特爾。",
      "ja": "みんな君の絵が大好きだよ、マートル。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I guess I just need to come out of Michelle a little more.",
      "zh": "我想我只是需要多一點勇氣。",
      "ja": "もう少し自分を出せばいいんだね。",
      "time": "00:06:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hehehe.",
      "zh": "呵呵。",
      "ja": "へへへ。",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mr. McNabbard, I'd say, expect a source.",
      "zh": "麥納巴德先生，我想說，期待一個來源。",
      "ja": "マクナバード先生、期待していいですよ。",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I mean, I can't wait to get a drawing.",
      "zh": "我的意思是，我迫不及待想看到畫了。",
      "ja": "絵を見るのが待ちきれません。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Myrtle, over here.",
      "zh": "默特爾，這邊。",
      "ja": "マートル、こっちだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, guys.",
      "zh": "嘿，大家。",
      "ja": "やあ、みんな。",
      "time": "00:06:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I sit with you?",
      "zh": "我可以跟你們坐一起嗎？",
      "ja": "一緒に座ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, of course.",
      "zh": "當然可以。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need.",
      "zh": "我需要。",
      "ja": "必要だよ。",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ooh, I like your wonder shark lunchbox, Danny.",
      "zh": "喔，我喜歡你的奇蹟鯊魚便當盒，丹尼。",
      "ja": "わあ、ダニーのワンダーシャークのお弁当箱いいね。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks, Sammy.",
      "zh": "謝謝，山米。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、サミー。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like your lunchbox, too.",
      "zh": "我也喜歡你的便當盒。",
      "ja": "君のお弁当箱も好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad!",
      "zh": "爸爸！",
      "ja": "パパ！",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It has dinosaurs on it!",
      "zh": "上面有恐龍！",
      "ja": "恐竜が描いてある！",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:07:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ooh, everyone's lunch looks so yummy.",
      "zh": "喔，大家的午餐看起來都好好吃。",
      "ja": "みんなのお弁当美味しそう。",
      "time": "00:07:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mine definitely is.",
      "zh": "我的肯定很好吃。",
      "ja": "僕のは絶対美味しいよ。",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a salad.",
      "zh": "是一份沙拉。",
      "ja": "サラダだよ。",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And my dad says salad is smart food, so I eat a lot of it.",
      "zh": "我爸爸說沙拉是聰明食物，所以我吃很多。",
      "ja": "パパがサラダは賢い食べ物だと言うから、たくさん食べてる。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know, so I can be smarter.",
      "zh": "你知道的，這樣我可以更聰明。",
      "ja": "賢くなれるからね。",
      "time": "00:07:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, smarter?",
      "zh": "我是說，更聰明？",
      "ja": "つまり、もっと賢く？",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, um, I almost forgot.",
      "zh": "哦，嗯，我差點忘了。",
      "ja": "ああ、うん、忘れるところだった。",
      "time": "00:07:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I brought some muffins to me and my grandma baked.",
      "zh": "我帶了一些我和奶奶烤的鬆餅。",
      "ja": "おばあちゃんと一緒に焼いたマフィンを持ってきたよ。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can all have some.",
      "zh": "你們都可以吃一些。",
      "ja": "みんなで食べてね。",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks, Myrtle.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，默特爾。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、マートル。",
      "time": "00:07:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're the best, Myrtle.",
      "zh": "你是最棒的，默特爾。",
      "ja": "マートル、君は最高だよ。",
      "time": "00:07:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, thanks.",
      "zh": "哦，謝謝。",
      "ja": "ああ、ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right, yummy, muffins.",
      "zh": "好吧，好吃的鬆餅。",
      "ja": "さあ、美味しいマフィンだ。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you have a nice lunch, everyone?",
      "zh": "大家午餐吃得愉快嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな、ランチは楽しかった？",
      "time": "00:07:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah!",
      "zh": "是的！",
      "ja": "うん！",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We did!",
      "zh": "我們有！",
      "ja": "楽しかったよ！",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's so hungry!",
      "zh": "真餓啊！",
      "ja": "お腹すいた！",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fantastic!",
      "zh": "太棒了！",
      "ja": "素晴らしい！",
      "time": "00:07:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, for our next lesson,",
      "zh": "現在，進入下一課，",
      "ja": "さて、次の授業は、",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "we're going to learn how to count to ten.",
      "zh": "我們要學習如何數到十。",
      "ja": "10まで数える方法を学びます。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, oh, I already know how to count to ten.",
      "zh": "哦，哦，我已經會數到十了。",
      "ja": "ああ、もう10まで数えられるよ。",
      "time": "00:07:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One, two, three, seven, four, eight.",
      "zh": "一，二，三，七，四，八。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん、なな、よん、はち。",
      "time": "00:07:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, I'm listening.",
      "zh": "好，我在聽。",
      "ja": "わかった、聞いてるよ。",
      "time": "00:08:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nice try, Oscar.",
      "zh": "不錯的嘗試，奧斯卡。",
      "ja": "いい挑戦だね、オスカー。",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's play a game.",
      "zh": "我們來玩個遊戲。",
      "ja": "ゲームをしよう。",
      "time": "00:08:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Shelley, look around the classroom and tell me what do you see one of.",
      "zh": "雪莉，看看教室周圍，告訴我你看到有一個什麼。",
      "ja": "シェリー、教室を見回して、一つだけ見えるものを教えて。",
      "time": "00:08:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me see here.",
      "zh": "讓我看看這裡。",
      "ja": "ここを見てみよう。",
      "time": "00:08:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I see what.",
      "zh": "我看到什麼。",
